description: On the instructions of boss Brad Rock, Park Rangers Jake Dakota and Duncan Stone (all three in non-sexual roles) warn camper Jessie Zane of a big-dicked pervert on the loose in the park. Rather than dissuading him from any outdoor encounters, the two men pique Jessie's interest as they describe the villain. When sexual predator Dak Ramsey comes around, Jessie pumps and fingers his tight ass -- inviting Dak to take it, which he promptly does, filling the forest with the heady sights and sounds of sex.
title: Ranger, Scene #01
